More Room - More Savings
------------------------http://www.aa.com 
If you've been waiting for low fares to your favorite travel destination, your wait is over. Now through April 10, 2002, American Airlines - the only Airline with MORE ROOM THROUGHOUT COACH, is now offering Spring Savings with our More Room - More Savings Sale. Save an additional 5% off published sale fares for online bookings for travel to exciting destinations throughout North America, Europe, the Caribbean, the Pacific, Central and South America, and Mexico. 
With fares like this to destinations like these, fly the only airline that offers MORE ROOM THROUGHOUT COACH for more Coach passengers. Visit www.aa.com for more details on travel dates and complete rules and restrictions. Here are just a few sample fares: 
